HEADWORD: Brickellia
<hw>Brickellia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>genus of herbs of SW America
having usually creamy florets followed by one-seeded fruits in a
prominent bristly sheath.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Brickelia</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
